	(209, 1, '2013-04-07 22:04:12', '2013-04-07 15:04:12', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="new-ct" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><strong>V&oacute;i mẫu legging n&agrave;y m&ugrave;a đ&ocirc;ng sẽ tr&agrave;n ngập phong c&aacute;ch, trẻ trung v&agrave; rất tiện lợi.</strong></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T17EAhXoJcXXXXXXXX_245601700-0-pix.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="T17EAhXoJcXXXXXXXX 245601700 0 pix Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1569" height="563" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T17EAhXoJcXXXXXXXX_245601700-0-pix.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="T17EAhXoJcXXXXXXXX_!!245601700-0-pix" width="550" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">Kiểu legging k&egrave;m v&aacute;y như thế n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng phải qu&aacute; mới mẻ nhưng năm nay, ch&uacute;ng đang trở lại với mật độ d&agrave;y v&agrave; nhiều kiểu d&aacute;ng&nbsp;<a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;" title="thời trang">thời trang</a>&nbsp;hơn. B&ecirc;n cạnh c&aacute;c mẫu legging &ndash; v&aacute;y m&agrave;u đen, x&aacute;m d&aacute;ng cơ bản, ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh sẽ thấy c&aacute;c kiểu ph&aacute; c&aacute;ch như legging &ndash; v&aacute;y nhung, legging &ndash; v&aacute;y kh&oacute;a k&eacute;o&hellip;</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1fXkiXnpfXXXXXXXX_929286868-0-pix.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="T1fXkiXnpfXXXXXXXX 929286868 0 pix Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1564" height="600" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1fXkiXnpfXXXXXXXX_929286868-0-pix.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="T1fXkiXnpfXXXXXXXX_!!929286868-0-pix" width="450" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">M&agrave;u trắng x&aacute;m n&agrave;y chỉ d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc; n&agrave;ng ch&acirc;n c&ograve; hương th&ocirc;i.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1LjMgXfRgXXXXXXXX_297648906-0-pix.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="T1LjMgXfRgXXXXXXXX 297648906 0 pix Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1565" height="550" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1LjMgXfRgXXXXXXXX_297648906-0-pix.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="T1LjMgXfRgXXXXXXXX_!!297648906-0-pix" width="550" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">Leeging k&egrave;m v&aacute;y chấm bi đ&aacute;ng y&ecirc;u m&agrave; lại rất dễ mix nữa.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1qEofXmBeXXXXXXXX_162767236-0-pix.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="T1qEofXmBeXXXXXXXX 162767236 0 pix Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1566" height="550" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1qEofXmBeXXXXXXXX_162767236-0-pix.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="T1qEofXmBeXXXXXXXX_!!162767236-0-pix" width="550" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">Thấp tho&aacute;ng tr&ecirc;n phố, người ta thấy cả những mẫu legging &ndash; v&aacute;y xẻ quyến rũ&hellip;</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1zWUfXg8fXXXXXXXX_262525147-0-pix.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="T1zWUfXg8fXXXXXXXX 262525147 0 pix Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1568" height="500" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1zWUfXg8fXXXXXXXX_262525147-0-pix.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="T1zWUfXg8fXXXXXXXX_!!262525147-0-pix" width="500" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">.. Hoặc lấp l&aacute;nh cực bắt mắt.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1xNciXfJcXXXXXXXX_315598210-0-pix.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="T1xNciXfJcXXXXXXXX 315598210 0 pix Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1567" height="550" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/T1xNciXfJcXXXXXXXX_315598210-0-pix.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="T1xNciXfJcXXXXXXXX_!!315598210-0-pix" width="550" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;">Th&ocirc;ng thường, với kiểu mốt 2 trong 1 n&agrave;y, phần v&aacute;y v&agrave; legging sẽ c&oacute; chung m&agrave;u sắc v&agrave; chất liệu. V&aacute;y c&oacute; thể c&aacute;ch điệu một ch&uacute;t như d&aacute;ng x&ograve;e, d&aacute;ng &ocirc;m, kh&oacute;a k&eacute;o, họa tiết nhỏ.</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-9.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="Untitled 9 Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1575" height="550" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-9.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="Untitled-9" width="600" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-8.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="Untitled 8 Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1574" height="550" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-8.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="Untitled-8" width="600" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-7.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="Untitled 7 Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1573" height="640" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-7.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="Untitled-7" width="552" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-61.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="Untitled 61 Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1572" height="640" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-61.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="Untitled-6" width="552" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"><a href="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-4.jpg" style="color: rgb(225, 26, 31); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="Untitled 4 Legging liền váy 2 trong 1 cho teengirl" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1570" height="600" src="http://tapchithoitrang.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Untitled-4.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: block; margin: 10px auto;" title="Untitled-4" width="552" /></a></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: right;">Theo ione.net</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="social bottom" style="